{"tid":1987192,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度封城一個月恆河水質達可飲用標準","createTime":"2020-04-24T10:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T05:26:52.000Z","uid":241764,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9d4711f7c2a39f018ede1455c287b58f12bca30e","tid":1987192,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:07:42.000Z","msg":"印度早前因應新型冠狀病毒疫情，宣布全國封城，為被公認全球污染最嚴重的河流之一的恆河，帶來意想不到的改變。<br />\n<br />\n印度Zee News報道，印度全國封城近一個月，人類在恆河一帶的活動大減，連帶環境污染問題亦得到改善。原本只適宜洗澡的河水，部分河段水質達到可飲用標準，是自2000年的首次。<br />\n<br />\n印度人相信恆河河水可以治病，所以經常有大量的人湧到恆河沐浴，加上遊客及河流沿岸居民，令恆河污染情況嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n有研究指恆河八成污染源頭都是來自人類，河水內含有大量細菌，水質只有B級，只適宜沐浴或其他用途。<br />\n<br />\n印度當局因應新冠病毒疫情，在3月底開始實施全國封城，措施維持至5月初。<br />\n<br />\n封城近一個月後，當局對恆河水質進行檢測。水質樣本來自北阿坎德省，相距約20公里的聖城赫爾德瓦爾及里希蓋什兩處位置，結果發現這個河段水質大為改善。<br />\n<br />\n數據顯示河水含氧量增加了20%，意味水底生物有足夠氧氣呼吸，水質亦達到A級標準，即是經過濾後適合飲用，是自2000年以來的首次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388823&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabknyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=dd0b8f30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388823&h=974bb6b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388823</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cff23acb2339f69685d78282a721e80c98c11f5","tid":1987192,"uid":291750,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:08:48.000Z","msg":"無可能，一定係神蹟"},{"pid":"4889b35fb2f837922a039be8196a48552897a531","tid":1987192,"uid":238415,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:12:43.000Z","msg":"解封完唔使幾個鐘咪又回復&quot;正常&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6243a6756d9d0cad0eb200215e5b2caac23a4a","tid":1987192,"uid":103916,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:13:32.000Z","msg":"你飲啦，我就唔飲啦。"},{"pid":"c2b5b87e891c53fbf298f7d6b8c9b34d3cb667e5","tid":1987192,"uid":48286,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:14:12.000Z","msg":"佢哋可飲用標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84fab7b2d7f4c0b030c5335d6bb64a4ea44fd33","tid":1987192,"uid":9726,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:14:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9009fca76258e03bfad351d64707a0990fc4e4c1","tid":1987192,"uid":20222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:28:43.000Z","msg":"gg 了<br />\n印度人要病死了"},{"pid":"3c542fe22ac4f7a8e671682f51eef628dfc6a132","tid":1987192,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:52:34.000Z","msg":"就算有認證，都唔會飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f3edbed188a6509c856e08164c74ceb426b593","tid":1987192,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T13:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a560b95e8096cce1a2f1b3d50fb635ec28190b50","tid":1987192,"uid":197826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T13:37:58.000Z","msg":"點有可能<br />\n又屎又尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9684856fef8056c6a1ae8c04206b8bcc23e30f56","tid":1987192,"uid":34177,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T13:38:32.000Z","msg":"諗起之前有巴打分享過去旅行飲左啖恆河水<br />\n之後個5日係醫院渡過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6cee4bf80ec0e398e341d393e2017fb0747220","tid":1987192,"uid":160930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9684856fef8056c6a1ae8c04206b8bcc23e30